# Scion book sources (this machine)

When implementing or changing character creation logic, data lists, or UI copy tied to rules, treat the **local PDF library** as the authority—not memory or the open web.

**Primary data canon for this app:** `SCION_Pandoras_Box_(Revised_Download).pdf` — use it first for **Boons**, **standard Purview Boon ladders**, **Knack compendium** (Calling chapters), **Birthrights** (types, dots, and most examples), and **Purview** write-ups that PB prints. When Origin or Hero gives a chargen *procedure* (e.g. Visitation order, Mortal steps) that PB only summarizes, follow the core book for that *procedure* but prefer **PB for the powers text** (costs, tags, Marvels, full Boon/Knack wording). If books disagree on a power, **default to Pandora’s Box (Revised)** unless the feature is explicitly MotW / Saints & Monsters / another supplement.

